{
  "stem": "26728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came back on another ship on-- for special training, was in the States for two months in 1943, let's see, '44-- and went back over on the Mariposa, which was another-- and it was a big cruiser, a big luxury liner, which was like the Queen Mary only smaller.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- well, it was-- they-- there was no way they could transport large numbers of men with airplanes in those days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They can do it now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have any-- they did-- they-- they just couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was logistically very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was only two ways to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One was to go the northern , route which was through from Maine to-- to Nova Scotia to Scotland and Greenland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the weather it was always terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were the German fighters in that vicinity watching for that to try to happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had you had a big disadvantage if you're in a passenger plane.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they didn't try to transport large numbers by air.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The other way was from-- from the-- from the coast down South to some islands-- [INAUDIBLE] right on the tip of my tongue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they do this now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's-- it's a-- it's a resort area now, and not Trinidad, but it's one of those Caribbean islands.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you hop scotched, and they did this with airplanes that had four engines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Navy ships?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--well, they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--didn't have any transports big enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would take 10,000, 15,000 men across at a time in the-- on the Queen Mary or on the Mariposa.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah and was-- and was assigned at-- at this point in time, I was a-- I was a replacement pilot, a utility replacement pilot, and went to a repo depot, they call them, a replacement depot.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
